{"tid":1708623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[捐獻師] [1111] 5%捐獻challenge","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T20:53:23.000Z","uid":267915,"like":154,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"36e17f823a283589a15acb79f896b01803d5744c","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"(借ac post) 手足，多謝你入黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本絲係在職和理非，今日1111好難捱，無奈始終會有手足各有原因，喺呢個日子未有罷工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹有個靈感，希望今日可以鼓勵大家做多少少，用唔同崗位的影響去略盡綿力，令前線得到多D應有的支援，再支持新工會、國際等等戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹呼籲大家今日計一計，將人工5%，捐俾自選機構。星火又得乜都得，你覺得有用就得，人工高就捐多D，如 <br />\n<br />\n人工$10000 X 5% = 500<br />\n<br />\n人工$50000 X 5% = 2500<br />\n<br />\n呢個數對打工仔一D都唔難做！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地目標係聽日(12/11) 2359截數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，13/11將會作結算。<br />\n<br />\n捐完影收據作証pm我就得，如有名記得**<strong>遮返名</strong>**。<br />\n<br />\n如果收到5000人的回應，就算每人捐一百，都已經有五十萬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，齊上齊落！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n快d share俾身邊的捐獻師接受5%挑戰，捐佢老母！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足就算有心無力都好，唔該幫手大大力share下面幅圖出去呀！！被捕手足好需要你地支援！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntg channel (公告): hk_5percent<br />\ntg group (加入): <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/M59_61JPxyE4sfBUMon1tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FM59_61JPxyE4sfBUMon1tw&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=5d721ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/M59_61JPxyE4sfBUMon1tw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ySbJq4V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FySbJq4V.jpg&h=ac5695a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d129524fba45557721ec8d689069aa6d127d33cc","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"自推10連 1/10"},{"pid":"bcaa88d4a69fbfafed33ecfbbe18d8ca862ac737","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"自推10連 2/10"},{"pid":"0ee9514a6cb7965eea07bccae6fdbd94e7da9017","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:42:53.000Z","msg":"自推十連 3/10"},{"pid":"c84f6d4be50b1aee43d6463f07d358519f9c3336","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"自推十連 4/10"},{"pid":"c22b64d3ac0eaedd949859a04be00d7feadcbd4e","tid":1708623,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:44:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連 5/10<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家幫幫手"},{"pid":"fe5bc6deac08c689d3c65efcf73fc9262fce0bfd","tid":1708623,"uid":130013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1cb92b1ceb743ec9ab9b0ba11f34a6755aeb615","tid":1708623,"uid":86750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:46:32.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"ac53eaff7724a2854ac576729d52ad02bccdd9d9","tid":1708623,"uid":130013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:47:32.000Z","msg":"等1